
{ Support for vim

  → https://github.com/luisjure/csound is a repository with *csound tools for → development/vim*.

}
{ Installing development


  On → Linux/distributions/Ubuntu:
code {
sudo apt-get install libcsound64-dev
code }
For `csound.hpp`, it also needs
code {
sudo apt-get install libcsnd-dev
code }
 
}
